  <entry>
    <title>Initial</title>
    <url>/2021/09/05/Initial/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Hello! You are reading <em>Olivier Jeannin</em>'s blog, and this is my very first proper post.</p>
<h2 id="what-happened-before-this-blog">What happened before this blog</h2>
<p>In fact, just two years ago, I tried to keep a blog site and worked really heard to learn how, though I did not actually get the key point then and gave it up.</p>
<p>During this summer vacation, which has just passed, I reviewed my earlier work and found it a piece of sh*t... So I just spent a while to learn to build a blog from scratch and tried around, and finally, finally, I can write a decent piece so as to kick the blog off.</p>
<h2 id="what-why-i-would-write">What &amp; Why I would write</h2>
<p>After this piece, you will see, hopefully, some notes on what I am learning at school, some notes on what I'm learning off scholl, my random thoughts, etc. I take them down mainly to stop me from learning without any notes and forgetting everything I have just got to know for, maybe, 2 months. You know, accordingly, recalling is the best known way to memorize information. And I also hope that blogging would make me a good note-taker. Apparently, I can practise some note-taking skills on it.</p>
<h2 id="last">Last</h2>
<p>At last, of course, I want whoever may see this blog to find something useful and enjoy it. We may not know each other, but I still find it satisfied should I be helpful to anyone.</p>
<p><strong><em>Wish you a good day,</em></strong></p>
<p><strong><em>Olivier</em></strong></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
